Package fun.connor.cafe.security.authentication

Provides the cafe.connor.fun APIs and implementations for user authentication.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SubjectFactory
    RequestGuardFactory for Subject classes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GoogleSignInAuthenticator
    The GoogleSignInAuthenticator authenticates Google-generated user credentials (in the form of a signed-id token) and extracts the user id string.
    GoogleSubjectFactory
    An implementation of SubjectFactory that uses the Google Client-ID service to authenticate Subjects using Google Id Tokens.
    Role
    A role to be consumed by authorization logic.
    Subject
    Authentication Subject.

Package fun.connor.cafe.security.authentication Description

Provides the cafe.connor.fun APIs and implementations for user authentication. Current implementation uses the Google Client Id Service.
